Shape (abstract)
  - radius: double
  - color: String
  + Shape(double radius, String color)
  + getArea(): double
  + getPerimeter(): double

Circle (concrete)
  - radius: double
  - color: String
  + Circle(double radius, String color)
  + getArea(): double
  + getPerimeter(): double

Rectangle (concrete)
  - width: double
  - height: double
  - color: String
  + Rectangle(double width, double height, String color)
  + getArea(): double
  + getPerimeter(): double